This directory is where the compiled WASM output is placed.

Run `./build_wasm.sh all` from the project root to build and copy files here.

Expected files after build:
- azahar.js        - Emscripten-generated JavaScript loader
- azahar.wasm      - Compiled WebAssembly binary
- azahar.html      - Emscripten-generated HTML (reference only)
- *.data           - Preloaded filesystem data (if any)
- *.worker.js      - Web Worker for threading
